---
// src/pages/Home.astro
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import LogoTemp from '../assets/logo_temp.png';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>ECV - Nathan Fourny</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Header -->
  <Header />

  <!-- Section Principale -->
  <main class="home-main">
    <div class="background-image"></div>
    <div class="content-overlay">
      <div class="intro-text">
        <h1>Bienvenue sur mon Portfolio</h1>
        <p>Je suis Nathan Fourny, développeur web passionné par la création de sites modernes et fonctionnels. Explorez mes projets et découvrez mon parcours. <br /> Ut in tempus orci. Proin id arcu laoreet dolor lacinia gravida. Cras ac egestas dolor. Aliquam vel leo nec libero tempor dictum ut quis justo. Etiam congue fringilla libero a interdum. In varius nunc id lectus dignissim, id interdum turpis condimentum. Curabitur in ligula ac enim pellentesque finibus ut eget lectus. Morbi interdum nisi dignissim lectus porttitor porttitor. Quisque aliquam, mi non dictum volutpat, mauris purus tempus est, vitae rhoncus felis nulla ac sem. Etiam tempus erat et maximus commodo. Nulla egestas ligula felis. <br /> udbiuzdbuqbdqzuid. dunz quidznuizdzui, duiquzidqui, duhqzuihdqui quiduiz duhdquz iuzqdudhzuidq uidhuidhzqu.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="profile-photo">
        <img src={LogoTemp.src} alt="Photo de Nathan Fourny" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <Footer />

  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600&display=swap');

    body, html {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      height: 100%;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .home-main {
      position: relative;
      height: 100vh;
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .background-image {
      background-image: url('../assets/background.jpg');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      height: 100%;
      width: 100%;
      z-index: -1;
    }

    .content-overlay {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      max-width: 1200px;
      width: 90%;
      height: 75%;
    }

    .intro-text {
      flex: 1;
      color: #000000;
      padding: 1rem;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      border-radius: 8px;
      height: 100%;
    }

    .intro-text h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .intro-text p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .profile-photo {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .profile-photo img {
      width: 250px;
      height: 250px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      object-fit: cover;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .profile-photo img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    @media (max-width: 992px) {
      .content-overlay {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .intro-text, .profile-photo {
        flex: none;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .profile-photo {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 576px) {
      .intro-text h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .intro-text p {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .profile-photo img {
        width: 200px;
        height: 200px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</body>
</html>
